        "Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew. (2026). <em>Swinglea glutinosa</em> (Blanco) Merr. <em>Plants of the World Online</em>. https://powo.science.kew.org/taxon/urn:lsid:ipni.org:names:775281-1",
